<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>iCommerce Account Activation</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Base */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            color: #333333;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        a {
            color: #0066CC;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0066CC;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f0f6ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px dashed #c2d8ff;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }
        /* Layout */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066CC 0%, #0047AB 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #eaeaea;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #0066CC;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .otp-instruction {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066CC;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .welcome-features {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .welcome-features div {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .welcome-features div:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #0066CC;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066CC 0%, #0047AB 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .support-info {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-body {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 26px;
                letter-spacing: 3px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <span class="email-logo">iCommerce</span>
            <h1>Welcome <%= name %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello ,</p>
            <p>
                Thank you for registering with iCommerce. We're excited to have you on board!
                To activate your account and start shopping, please use the following verification code:
            </p>
            
            <h2><%= otp %></h2>
            
            <div class="otp-instruction">
                <p><strong>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="welcome-features">
                <p>Once your account is activated, you'll be able to:</p>
                <div>Browse thousands of products across multiple categories</div>
                <div>Save items to your wishlist for later</div>
                <div>Enjoy fast and secure checkout</div>
                <div>Track your orders in real-time</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="support-info">
                <p>If you did not register for a iCommerce account, please ignore this email.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>© 2025 iCommerce. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Help Center</a> • 
                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> • 
                <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
            </div>
            <p>
                Contact us at <a href="mailto:rrajchaudhary.hajipur@gmail.com">rrajchaudhary.hajipur@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for an iCommerce account.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
